These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
City: boston, hamburg, rome, colone, edinburgh
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bluemaster, bolivar, oliveros, vegafina
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, lacrosse, skiing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the bluemaster-smoker is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the british##1
10. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| City         | hamburg  | boston    | colone | rome    | edinburgh  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Cigar           | chaman     | vegafina     | oliveros  | bluemaster   | bolivar    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skiing    | cycling | baseball  | swimming |

