.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
House: ranch-style, futuristic, art-deco, wooden, craftsman
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, baking, singing, filmmaking, chess
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the wooden house is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the russian is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the futuristic house##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| House           | futuristic   | art-deco | craftsman    | wooden | ranch-style |
| Hobby   | singing | filmmaking     | chess | video-games    | baking  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

