.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, january, may, march, november
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, trance, jazz, reggae, disco
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of trance##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Birthday         | january | november | march  | may   | august    |
| Music-Genre   | trance        | disco | country | reggae    | jazz   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

