The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, horror, scientific, superhero, time-travel
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, entrepreneur, architect, pilot, mechanic
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 3. the entrepreneur is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the freelancer is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the pilot##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the pilot is on the left of the palace house##1
10. the futuristic house is the architect##1
11. the craftsman house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| House          | victorian        | palace       | art-deco | craftsman   | futuristic  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
| Job   | pilot         | mechanic     | entrepreneur | freelancer | architect     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

