 9. the police-officer is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the project-manager is in the middle##1
11. the fan of techno is on the left of the project-manager##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

