 3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of country##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person drinking water is the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to paris is the person drinking juice##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan of folk##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
13. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

