 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is the person playing bridge##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is chess##1
