10. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
11. the person playing go is on the far left##1
12. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person driving the taxi##1
13. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
