5 different pets are kept: cat, fish, mouse, rabbit, rat
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar, havana, fonseca, oliveros
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the fonseca-smoker##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is the bongani-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
11. the person who likes ebony is the owner of the rat##1
12. the owner of the cat is the person who likes emerald##1
13. the owner of the rat is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Hobby         | hiking   | dancing   | reading   | sudoku     | gardening |
