 5. the fisherman is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the electrician is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the fisherman##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the accountant##1
12. the manager is the person traveling to miami##1
13. the accountant is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola       | milk         | juice  | iced-tea |
| Job   | manager  | scientist | electrician | fisherman  | accountant  |
| City   | miami    | new-york    | london        | marseilles | venice     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

