.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, sports, thriller, western
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, doctor, coach, scientist, analyst
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, bike, ship, subway, van
 1. the scientist is on the right of the analyst##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 3. the coach is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the analyst is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the fan of country##1
 9. the doctor is in the middle##1
10. the architect is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the scientist##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
