 3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is the person watching thriller movies##1
