.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, western, crime, fantasy, spy
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, ebony, chestnut, white, purple
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes purple##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the far right##1
12. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
13. the person who likes aquamarine is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person who likes white is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | crime           | western   | spy   | fantasy       | mystery  |
| Color   | ebony       | aquamarine | chestnut | white     | purple   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 